org.apache.hadoop.yarn.server.nodemanager.containermanager.linux.privileged

Class PrivilegedOperation

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.apache.hadoop.yarn.server.nodemanager.containermanager.linux.privileged.PrivilegedOperation

  • @InterfaceAudience.Private
 @InterfaceStability.Unstable
public class PrivilegedOperation
extends Object
    Represents operations that require higher system privileges - e.g creating cgroups, launching containers as specified users, 'tc' commands etc that are completed using the container-executor binary
